## ✅ Production Readiness Checklist
| Check | Status | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| `STRATA_AI_ENV=prod` | ☐ | Disables `/docs`, backtraces, diagnostic logs |
| `STRATA_AI_OTLP_ENDPOINT` | ☐ | OTel exports to collector (not console) |
| `STRATA_AI_LOG_SERIALIZE=true` | ☐ | JSON logs for ELK/Datadog/Splunk |
| Health probe active | ☐ | `curl /health` returns `{"status":"ok"}` |
| Graceful shutdown tested | ☐ | `SIGTERM` → 30s drain → clean exit |
| `--factory` flag used | ☐ | Ensures per-worker app initialization |
| PII/Guardrails enabled | ☐ | `pii_sensitive=True` on sensitive endpoints |
| Rate limiting configured | ☐ | Via `app/core/middleware.py` or ingress gateway |